"main"><div data-enable-parallax="0" data-parallax-speed="0.5" data-background-images="{}" data-background-type="image" data-video-loop="true" data-video-play-only-visible="true" data-video-lazy-load="true" data-video-fallback-src="" data-video-fallback-src-mobile="" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="inner" data-pb-style="FI1FPM0"><div data-content-type="divider" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><hr data-element="line" data-pb-style="HF4D6WM"></div></div></div><div data-content-type="row" data-appearance="contained" data-element="main"><div class="mobile-hide" data-enable-parallax="1" data-parallax-speed="0.1" data-background-images="{\&quot;desktop_image\&quot;:\&quot;{{media url=.renditions/wysiwyg/landing/about-me/brains.png}}\&quot;}" data-background-type="image" data-video-loop="true" data-video-play-only-visible="true" data-video-lazy-load="true" data-video-fallback-src="" data-video-fallback-src-mobile="" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="inner" data-pb-style="FUSJHDK"><div class="pagebuilder-column-group" data-background-images="{}" data-content-type="column-group" data-appearance="default" data-grid-size="12" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main" data-pb-style="T1D9VTB"><div class="pagebuilder-column-line" data-content-type="column-line" data-element="main" data-pb-style="GJHHOFX"><div class="pagebuilder-column" data-content-type="column" data-appearance="full-height" data-background-images="{}" data-width-mobile="" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main" data-pb-style="VAYHFRN"><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><h3 style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #e67e23;">1. <a tabindex="0" href="https://www.lacuracaonline.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LaCuracaOnline</a> &amp; <a tabindex="0" href="https://www.radioshackla.com/">RadioShack LA</a></span></h3></div><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><p style="text-align: left;">My first steps with Magento were with Back-End tasks for this websites which belongs to Unicomer, a very important group in the Central American region.<br>The initial tasks were based on investigating and fixing bugs, admin settings such as ACL, default settings, etc. The languages used were PHP (MVC), XML, JSON.&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Thanks to my academic background and being a professional graphic designer with a lot of experience, I started having Front-End assignments: where we can list general style adjustments, code improvement, suggestions based on UX patterns .</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">The language I mainly worked on was LESS (CSS) and some lines of PHTML and JS.</p></div><div data-content-type="divider" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><hr data-element="line" data-pb-style="MVKM71T"></div><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><h3 style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #e67e23;">3. <a id="GONBYP1" tabindex="0" href="https://www.paruolo.com.ar/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Paruolo</a></span></h3></div><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><p style="text-align: left;">My contribution to stand out in my first challenge with a new client of the company was to help mates for some hours with style sheets and behavior such as Swatches, Zoom on the PDP photo, etc.</p></div><div data-content-type="divider" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><hr data-element="line" data-pb-style="FJX1RG9"></div><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><h3 style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #e67e23;">5. <a id="GONBYP1" tabindex="0" href="https://ar.isadoraonline.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Isadora</a> &amp; <a tabindex="0" href="https://ar.todomoda.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Todomoda</a></span></h3></div><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><p style="text-align: left;">I joined the team developing the site for these Blue Star Group brands to start learning how the proprietary Front-End Suite works.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Thanks to this, I know how the company offers a more agile, professional and cross-site solution, achieving some development solutions just by configuring this tool.</p></div></div><div class="pagebuilder-column" data-content-type="column" data-appearance="full-height" data-background-images="{}" data-width-mobile="" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main" data-pb-style="T6TOMRK"></div><div class="pagebuilder-column" data-content-type="column" data-appearance="full-height" data-background-images="{}" data-width-mobile="" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main" data-pb-style="WQ1RH6X"><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><h3 style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #e67e23;">2. <a tabindex="0" href="https://www.jazminchebar.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jazmin Chebar</a></span></h3></div><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><p style="text-align: right;">After a quarter, I was awarded with the opportunity to be part of the development team for one of the most outstanding clients. Jazmin Chebar is a project with a long history in the company with many custom developments. They not only set trends with their clothes but also with their website.</p>
<p style="text-align: right;">Soon after I had a great challenge: carry out the complete redesign of the <a tabindex="0" href="https://www.jazminchebar.com/en_us/customer/account/login/">My Account section</a>.<br>Here I began to work hard with the templates, layouts, icons, fonts and I began to have more direct contact with the client, for example, to get feedback on the proposed mobile screens.</p>
<p style="text-align: right;">I worked for this client a considerable time having new challenges such as the development of several email templates (from Magento and third-party marketing), <a tabindex="0" href="https://www.jazminchebar.com.ar/digital-point">landing</a> <a tabindex="0" href="https://www.jazminchebar.com.ar/jazmin-circular">pages</a> (with PageBuilder), page layouts, two framework upgrades, more UI redesigns, fonts, svg, bitmaps, behavior with JS, jQuery, KnockOutJS, mixins, translations, etc, etc.</p></div><div data-content-type="divider" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><hr data-element="line" data-pb-style="OX123CS"></div><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><h3 style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #e67e23;">4. <a id="A7E8ISG" tabindex="0" href="https://www.devre.la/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Devre</a></span></h3></div><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><p style="text-align: right;">Another fashion client where I did CMS layouts and email templates for a short time. Highlighting my first meeting with Magento 1.</p></div><div data-content-type="divider" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><hr data-element="line" data-pb-style="FWH680U"></div><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><h3 style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #e67e23;">6. EFE Group</span></h3></div><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><p style="text-align: right;">This year began with another great challenge: joining the development team of a new client. Grupo EFE is another very important appliance seller with a significant testing team.</p>
<p style="text-align: right;">Thanks to this project I have more experience in more detailed delivery times, several tickets daily, etc.<br>I am currently working with the advantages that the latest version of Magento and our Front-End Suite provide.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-content-type="row" data-appearance="contained" data-element="main"><div class="desktop-hide" data-enable-parallax="1" data-parallax-speed="0.1" data-background-images="{}" data-background-type="image" data-video-loop="true" data-video-play-only-visible="true" data-video-lazy-load="true" data-video-fallback-src="" data-video-fallback-src-mobile="" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="inner" data-pb-style="WF2W2DK"><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><h3 style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #e67e23;">1. <a tabindex="0" href="https://www.lacuracaonline.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LaCuracaOnline</a> &amp; <a tabindex="0" href="https://www.radioshackla.com/">RadioShack LA</a></span></h3></div><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><p style="text-align: left;">My first steps with Magento were with Back-End tasks for this websites which belongs to Unicomer, a very important group in the Central American region.<br>The initial tasks were based on investigating and fixing bugs, admin settings such as ACL, default settings, etc. The languages used were PHP (MVC), XML, JSON.&nbsp;</p>
