<p style="text-align: left;">The language I mainly worked on was LESS (CSS) and some lines of PHTML and JS.</p></div><div data-content-type="divider" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><hr data-element="line" data-pb-style="STU00IR"></div></div></div><div data-content-type="row" data-appearance="contained" data-element="main"><div class="desktop-hide" data-enable-parallax="0" data-parallax-speed="0.5" data-background-images="{}" data-background-type="image" data-video-loop="true" data-video-play-only-visible="true" data-video-lazy-load="true" data-video-fallback-src="" data-video-fallback-src-mobile="" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="inner" data-pb-style="IMGTKER"><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><h3 style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #e67e23;">2. <a tabindex="0" href="https://www.jazminchebar.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jazmin Chebar</a></span></h3></div><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><p style="text-align: left;">After a quarter, I was awarded with the opportunity to be part of the development team for one of the most outstanding clients. Jazmin Chebar is a project with a long history in the company with many custom developments. They not only set trends with their clothes but also with their website.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Soon after I had a great challenge: carry out the complete redesign of the <a tabindex="0" href="https://www.jazminchebar.com/en_us/customer/account/login/">My Account section</a>.<br>Here I began to work hard with the templates, layouts, icons, fonts and I began to have more direct contact with the client, for example, to get feedback on the proposed mobile screens.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">I worked for this client a considerable time having new challenges such as the development of several email templates (from Magento and third-party marketing), <a tabindex="0" href="https://www.jazminchebar.com.ar/digital-point">landing</a> <a tabindex="0" href="https://www.jazminchebar.com.ar/jazmin-circular">pages</a> (with PageBuilder), page layouts, two framework upgrades, more UI redesigns, fonts, svg, bitmaps, behavior with JS, jQuery, KnockOutJS, mixins, translations, etc, etc.</p></div><div data-content-type="divider" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><hr data-element="line" data-pb-style="VV540FS"></div></div></div><div data-content-type="row" data-appearance="contained" data-element="main"><div class="desktop-hide" data-enable-parallax="0" data-parallax-speed="0.5" data-background-images="{}" data-background-type="image" data-video-loop="true" data-video-play-only-visible="true" data-video-lazy-load="true" data-video-fallback-src="" data-video-fallback-src-mobile="" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="inner" data-pb-style="I701XEL"><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><h3 style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #e67e23;">3. <a id="GONBYP1" tabindex="0" href="https://www.paruolo.com.ar/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Paruolo</a></span></h3></div><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><p style="text-align: left;">My contribution to stand out in my first challenge with a new client of the company was to help mates for some hours with style sheets and behavior such as Swatches, Zoom on the PDP photo, etc.</p></div></div></div><div data-content-ty