" data-element="main"><p style="text-align: left;">Another fashion client where I did CMS layouts and email templates for a short time. Highlighting my first meeting with Magento 1.</p></div><div data-content-type="divider" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><hr data-element="line" data-pb-style="ANHXED7"></div></div></div><div data-content-type="row" data-appearance="contained" data-element="main"><div class="desktop-hide" data-enable-parallax="0" data-parallax-speed="0.5" data-background-images="{}" data-background-type="image" data-video-loop="true" data-video-play-only-visible="true" data-video-lazy-load="true" data-video-fallback-src="" data-video-fallback-src-mobile="" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="inner" data-pb-style="JAXW4N8"><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><h3 style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #e67e23;">5. <a id="GONBYP1" tabindex="0" href="https://ar.isadoraonline.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Isadora</a> &amp; <a tabindex="0" href="https://ar.todomoda.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Todomoda</a></span></h3></div><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><p style="text-align: left;">I joined the team developing the site for these Blue Star Group brands to start learning how the proprietary Front-End Suite works.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Thanks to this, I know how the company offers a more agile, professional and cross-site solution, achieving some development solutions just by configuring this tool.</p></div><div data-content-type="divider" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><hr data-element="line" data-pb-style="UTJU747"></div></div></div><div data-content-type="row" data-appearance="contained" data-element="main"><div class="desktop-hide" data-enable-parallax="0" data-parallax-speed="0.5" data-background-images="{}" data-background-type="image" data-video-loop="true" data-video-play-only-visible="true" data-video-lazy-load="true" data-video-fallback-src="" data-video-fallback-src-mobile="" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="inner" data-pb-style="FGL1A5U"><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><h3 style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #e67e23;">6. EFE Group</span></h3></div><div data-content-type="text" data-appearance="default" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><p style="text-align: left;">This year began with another great challenge: joining the development team of a new client. Grupo EFE is another very important appliance seller with a significant testing team.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Thanks to this project I have more experience in more detailed delivery times, several tickets daily, etc.<br>I am currently working with the advantages that the latest version of Magento and our Front-End Suite provide.</p></div></div></div><div data-content-type="row" data-appearance="contained" data-element="main"><div data-enable-parallax="0" data-parallax-speed="0.5" data-background-images="{}" data-background-type="image" data-video-loop="true" data-video-play-only-visible="true" data-video-lazy-load="true" data-video-fallback-src="" data-video-fallback-src-mobile="" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="inner" data-pb-style="CWKRL2G"><div class="pagebuilder-slider mobile-hide" data-content-type="slider" data-appearance="default" data-autoplay="true" data-autoplay-speed="3000" data-fade="true" data-infinite-loop="true" data-show-arrows="false" data-show-dots="true" data-margins-and-padding-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-items-desktop="1" data-items-tablet="1" data-items-mobile="1" data-items-mobile-small="1" data-hide-arrows-mobile="0" data-hide-arrows-desktop="0" data-hide-dots-mobile="0" data-hide-dots-desktop="0" data-stage-padding="0" data-stage-padding-left="" data-stage-padding-left-desktop="" data-stage-padding-right="" data-stage-padding-right-desktop="" data-element="main" data-pb-style="MJUD7G6"><div data-content-type="slide" data-slide-name="" data-appearance="poster" data-show-button="never" data-show-overlay="never" data-margins-mobile="{}" data-hide-mobile="0" data-hide-desktop="0" data-element="main"><div data-element="empty_link"><div class="pagebuilder-slide-wrapper" data-background-images="{\&quot;desktop_image\&quot;:\&quot;{{media url=.renditions/wysiwyg/landing/about-me/bnr-1_lco.png}}\&quot;}" data-background-type="image" data-video-loop="true" data-video-play-only-visible="true" data-video-lazy-load="true" data-video-fallback